This README.md file provides all the necessary instructions for setting up, configuring, and running the Vendhan InfoTech website.

Vendhan InfoTech - Corporate Website

Vendhan InfoTech is a women-led IT powerhouse specializing in Custom Software, AI/ML Solutions, Cloud Digital Transformation, and high-precision BPO services. This repository contains the complete frontend and Node.js backend.

🚀 Features

Modern Responsive Design: Fully optimized for Desktop, Tablet, and Mobile.

Node.js v24 Compatible: Custom routing logic to handle the strictest path-parsing requirements.

Automated Contact Form: Sends emails directly to the administration using Nodemailer and Gmail.

Clean Architecture: Separation of concerns with a dedicated public folder for assets and a robust server.js for logic.

🛠️ Tech Stack

Frontend: HTML5, CSS3 (Modern Grid/Flexbox), JavaScript (ES6+).

Backend: Node.js, Express.js.

Email Service: Nodemailer (configured for Gmail App Passwords).

Environment Management: dotenv.

